<tbody valign="top"><row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0">1.</entry>
<entry align="left" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col2" rowsep="0">Summary note</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry align="left" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col3" rowsep="0"><emph typestyle="ib">Assessment of damages and value of goods &#x2014; Rules 30.1&#x2013;30.3</emph></entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry align="justify" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col4" rowsep="0">These rules govern the procedure where judgment is given for damages, or for the value of goods, to be assessed.</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0">2.</entry>
<entry align="left" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col2" rowsep="0">Application</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry align="justify" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col2" rowsep="0">This Part applies to all courts in <ci:cite searchtype="LEG-REF"><ci:content><remotelink dpsi="05CC" refpt="UCPN.CPA.CPAN05.SCH1" remotekey1="REFPTID" service="DOC-ID">Schedule 1</remotelink></ci:content></ci:cite>
of the CPA: see r 1.5 and Sch 1.</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0">3.</entry>
<entry align="left" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col2" rowsep="0">Historical note</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="0"><entry colsep="0" morerows="0" rowsep="0"/>
<entry align="justify" colsep="0" morerows="0" nameend="col5" namest="col2" rowsep="0">The Part is substantially based on the former SCR Part 35, DCR Part 27 and LCR Part 22.</entry>
</row>
